<h3 id="mp-5-4-control-enhancement-m-h">MP-5 (4) Control Enhancement (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization employs cryptographic mechanisms to protect the confidentiality and integrity of information stored on digital media during transport outside of controlled areas.</p>

