<h3 id="mp-7-media-use-l-m-h">MP-7 Media Use (L) (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization [Selection: restricts; prohibits] the use of [Assignment: organization-defined types of information system media] on [Assignment: organization-defined information systems or system components] using [Assignment: organization-defined security safeguards].</p>

